Introduction
In this assignment, you will use the MERN stack to write a Single Page Application (SPA) that tracks exercises completed by a user. You will use React for the frontend user interface app. You will write a REST API using Node and Express for the backend web service using Model View Controller (MVC) methods. You will use MongoDB for data persistence.

This is the "Portfolio Assignment" for the course. This means that you are allowed to post the entirety of the assignment publicly (e.g., GitHub, personal website, etc.) after the term ends. You can use this as an opportunity to showcase your work to potential employers. 

Be sure to periodically review Assignment 9: FAQs and Tips thread in the Ed discussion board (pinned at the top of the feed). 

