** Validation
The code to validate the request body can be from scratch, or by using the express-validator.Links to an external site. Here are some guidelines to use as comments as you write the code:

Ensure all required fields (except date) are present.
Ensure name is not empty.
Ensure reps is greater than 0.
Ensure weight is equal to or greater than 0.
Ensure unit is one of these values: "kgs", "lbs", or "miles".
If date is provided, ensure it is valid.
Date.parse() returns NaN if the string is not a valid date.
The acceptable format is ISO 8601 (e.g., "2025-08-27T00:00:00Z") or "YYYY-MM-DD".
